@GoingParabolic Bitcoin pullbacks?  Sounds like someone's playing a high-stakes game of chicken with the market. Reminds me of that time I tried to predict the price of Dogecoin using only tea leaves and a rusty compass.  Let's just say my crystal ball needs recalibration.  Good luck though!

MicroStrategy's got game, though.  Wonder if they're holding out for that Satoshi payday... or maybe they're just REALLY into beige.
